      <title>Golang库之mergo</title>
      <link href="posts/b85c60c3.html"/>
      <url>posts/b85c60c3.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="🔥-项目仓库">🔥 项目仓库</h2><a class="ghcard" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/imdario/mergo"><img src="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/pin/?username=imdario&repo=mergo&theme=solarized-light&show_owner=true" class="lazyload placeholder" data-srcset="https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/pin/?username=imdario&repo=mergo&theme=solarized-light&show_owner=true" srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/XuxuGood/cdn@master/blogImages/site-img/img-loading.gif"/></a><h2 id="🔥-安装">🔥 安装</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">go get github.com/imdario/mergo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="🔥-使用">🔥 使用</h2><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> (</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;fmt&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;github.com/imdario/mergo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;log&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> person <span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">Age <span class="keyword">int</span></span><br><span class="line">Name <span class="keyword">string</span></span><br><span class="line">Hobby <span class="keyword">string</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> tomPerson = person&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Age:   <span class="number">18</span>,</span><br><span class="line">Name:  <span class="string">&quot;tom&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">Hobby: <span class="string">&quot;basketball&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>  &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> demoPerson person</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> err := mergo.Merge(&amp;demoPerson, tomPerson); err != <span class="literal">nil</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">log.Fatalln(err)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson age:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Age)</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson name:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Name)</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson hobby:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Hobby)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> p = <span class="built_in">make</span>(<span class="keyword">map</span>[<span class="keyword">string</span>]<span class="keyword">interface</span>&#123;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> err := mergo.Map(&amp;p, tomPerson); err != <span class="literal">nil</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">log.Fatal(err)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(p)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用非常简单，<code>mergo</code>提供了两个接口：</p><ul><li><code>Mergo</code>：合并两个相同类型的<code>struct</code>和<code>map</code></li><li><code>Map</code>：在<code>struct</code>和<code>map</code>之间赋值</li></ul><p>参数1是目标对象，参数2是源对象，这两个函数的功能就是将源对象中的字段复制到目标对象的对应字段上</p><p>运行上面的代码结果为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demoPerson age: 18</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson name: tom</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson hobby: basketball</span><br><span class="line">map[age:18 hobby:basketball name:tom]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="🔥-高级选项">🔥 高级选项</h2><p>如果仅仅是复制结构体，为啥不直接写<code>demoPerson = tomPerson</code>呢？<code>mergo</code>提供了很多选项</p><h3 id="🔔-覆盖">🔔 覆盖</h3><p>默认情况下，如果目标对象的字段已经设置了，那么<code>Mergo</code>/<code>Map</code>不会用源对象中的字段替换它，我们在上面的代码<code>var demoPerson person</code>下加一行</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demoPerson.Age = <span class="number">20</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再看看运行结果：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demoPerson age: 20</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson name: tom</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson hobby: basketball</span><br><span class="line">map[age:18 hobby:basketball name:tom]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>demoPerson</code>的<code>Age</code>为20，我们会发现源对象的<code>Age</code>并未覆盖<code>demoPerson</code>的<code>Age</code></p><p>我们可以通过选项来改变这个行为，调用<code>Mergo</code>/<code>Map</code>时，传入<code>WithOverride</code>，那么就会覆盖</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> err := mergo.Merge(&amp;demoPerson, tomPerson, mergo.WithOverride); err != <span class="literal">nil</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">log.Fatalln(err)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时的输出结果为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demoPerson age: 18</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson name: tom</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson hobby: basketball</span><br><span class="line">map[age:18 hobby:basketball name:tom]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="🔔-切片">🔔 切片</h3><p>如果某个字段是一个切片，使用覆盖和不覆盖都不合适，此时我们就需要使用<code>WithAppendSlice</code>选项将源对象切片中的值添加到目标对象的字段中</p><p>修改上面的代码</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> (</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;fmt&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;github.com/imdario/mergo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;log&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> person <span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">Age <span class="keyword">int</span></span><br><span class="line">Name <span class="keyword">string</span></span><br><span class="line">Hobbies []<span class="keyword">string</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> tomPerson = person&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Age:   <span class="number">18</span>,</span><br><span class="line">Name:  <span class="string">&quot;tom&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">Hobbies: []<span class="keyword">string</span>&#123;<span class="string">&quot;basketball&quot;</span>&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>  &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> demoPerson person</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">demoPerson.Hobbies = []<span class="keyword">string</span>&#123;<span class="string">&quot;football&quot;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> err := mergo.Merge(&amp;demoPerson, tomPerson, mergo.WithAppendSlice); err != <span class="literal">nil</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">log.Fatalln(err)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson age:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Age)</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson name:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Name)</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson hobbies:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Hobbies)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时的输出结果为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demoPerson age: 18</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson name: tom</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson hobbies: [football basketball]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以看到，源对象中的值添加到了目标对象中了</p><h3 id="🔔-空值覆盖">🔔 空值覆盖</h3><p>默认情况下，如果源对象中的字段为空值（数字为0，字符串为”“等），即使我们使用了<code>WithOverride</code>选项也不会覆盖，下面这两个选项是强制这种情况下也覆盖：</p><ul><li><code>WithOverrideEmptySlice</code>：源对象的空切片覆盖目标对象的对应字段</li><li><code>WithOverwriteWithEmptyValue</code>：源对象的空值会覆盖目标对象的对应字段，这个对切片也有效果</li></ul><p>这两个选项必须和<code>WithOverride</code>一起使用</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> (</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;fmt&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;github.com/imdario/mergo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;log&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> person <span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">Age <span class="keyword">int</span></span><br><span class="line">Name <span class="keyword">string</span></span><br><span class="line">Hobbies []<span class="keyword">string</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> tomPerson = person&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Age:   <span class="number">18</span>,</span><br><span class="line">Name:  <span class="string">&quot;tom&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>  &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> demoPerson person</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">demoPerson.Hobbies = []<span class="keyword">string</span>&#123;<span class="string">&quot;football&quot;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> err := mergo.Merge(&amp;demoPerson, tomPerson, mergo.WithOverwriteWithEmptyValue); err != <span class="literal">nil</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">log.Fatalln(err)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson age:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Age)</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson name:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Name)</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;demoPerson hobbies:&quot;</span>, demoPerson.Hobbies)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上代码输出：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">demoPerson age: 18</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson name: tom</span><br><span class="line">demoPerson hobbies: []</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="🔔-类型检查">🔔 类型检查</h3><p>这个主要用在<code>map</code>之间的赋值，因为<code>mergo</code>在两个结构体之间赋值必须要求两个结构体的类型相同，没有检查的必要</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">m1 := <span class="built_in">make</span>(<span class="keyword">map</span>[<span class="keyword">string</span>]<span class="keyword">interface</span>&#123;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">m1[<span class="string">&quot;key&quot;</span>] = []<span class="keyword">int64</span>&#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">m2 := <span class="built_in">make</span>(<span class="keyword">map</span>[<span class="keyword">string</span>]<span class="keyword">interface</span>&#123;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">m2[<span class="string">&quot;key&quot;</span>] = []<span class="keyword">int</span>&#123;<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> err := mergo.Map(&amp;m1, &amp;m2, mergo.WithOverride); err != <span class="literal">nil</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">log.Fatalln(err)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(m1)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上代码输出为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">map[key:[2 3]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上代码中的<code>map</code>类型为<code>map[string]interface&#123;&#125;</code>，所以默认情况下，<code>map</code>切片类型不一致也是可以赋值的</p><p>如果添加<code>mergo.WithTypeCheck</code>选项，则会抛出错误</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cannot override two slices with different type ([]int, []int64)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="🔥-注意事项">🔥 注意事项</h2><ul><li><code>mergo</code>不会赋值非导出字段</li><li><code>map</code>中对应的键名首字母为转为小写</li><li><code>mergo</code>可以嵌套赋值</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Golang </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
